abstract: >-
  An open dataset of U.S. public-company equity stakes in Anthropic and OpenAI,
  collected from primary SEC filings (10-K / 10-Q / 8-K), public press releases,
  and court records. Each row is tagged with a confidence flag (V verified,
  P probable, S speculative). Includes a curated point-in-time snapshot,
  a machine-extracted panel from real SEC filings, and a catalog of primary
  funding rounds and Big Tech follow-on commitments.
